&lt;p data-start=&quot;0&quot; data-end=&quot;242&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;This internship is a &lt;strong data-start=&quot;21&quot; data-end=&quot;89&quot;&gt;hands-on testing role during a fast-paced product release period&lt;/strong&gt;. You’ll work closely with engineers to &lt;strong data-start=&quot;129&quot; data-end=&quot;206&quot;&gt;validate builds, run regression tests, debug issues, and document defects&lt;/strong&gt; to help maintain product stability.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;244&quot; data-end=&quot;338&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;It’s &lt;strong data-start=&quot;249&quot; data-end=&quot;303&quot;&gt;execution-focused (not research or model training)&lt;/strong&gt;, but gives you strong exposure to:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul data-start=&quot;339&quot; data-end=&quot;503&quot;&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot; data-section-id=&quot;bqkviu&quot; data-start=&quot;339&quot; data-end=&quot;391&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;AI-driven product development and release cycles&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot; data-section-id=&quot;jwejik&quot; data-start=&quot;392&quot; data-end=&quot;443&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Pull request validation and release engineering&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot; data-section-id=&quot;inhbyv&quot; data-start=&quot;444&quot; data-end=&quot;503&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;How real-world agentic AI systems behave and are tested&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;505&quot; data-end=&quot;746&quot; data-is-last-node=&quot;&quot; data-is-only-node=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;The role is designed to make an immediate impact while helping you learn how AI systems are built and shipped—especially in healthcare. High-performing interns may also contribute ideas to improve testing and automation as the system scales.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
